<item>
            <title>[LU-3858] sanity test_27A: @@@@@@ FAIL: stripe count -1 != 1</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3858</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sanity 27A failed when we tried to run tests. We found that after clearing the stripe of Lustre root directry, it will takes seconds before the stripe is updated actually. We can reproduce the problem easily by running the script attached.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The delay of stripe updating may due to the delay of config log processing. It may not be easy to change this behavior, so I changed the test suit. I will push the patch soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
